Class AbstractConfig2019<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.record.daqconfig2019.AbstractConfig2019<E>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ESBCutConfig2019, FEEPrecaleConfig2019, FEETriggerConfig2019, HodoEcalCoincidence2019, LBOCutConfig2019, MultiplicityTriggerConfig2019, PairTriggerConfig2019, PDECutConfig2019, SinglesTriggerConfig2019, UBOCutConfig2019, ULBCutConfig2019

    abstract class AbstractConfig2019<E>
extends Object
    Abstract class AbstractConfig2019 holds a given number of values and allows implementing classes to access them. It also stores whether the configuration object is enabled.
